Qh3 Na6 12. Be2 h5 $1 13. Bd1 (13. f4 {keeps the equality.}) 13... Bd7 14. Nge2
Nb4 15. f4 $1 e4 16. Nc1 $2 {White should castle and reorganise.} (16. O-O $1
O-O-O 17. a3 $1 Na6 {defends well.}) 16... O-O-O 17. a3 Na6 18. b4 Bg7 $1 19.
Rb1 Rdg8 20. N1e2 b6 21. b5 $5 Nc7 22. Qe3 $6 Bf6 23. Qh3 $6 {
