little money. There was no Maroczy for Hungary, no Marshall for the USA, no
Rubinstein and Tartakower for Poland and no Grünfeld for Austria. Nevertheless,
Kashdan could shine as a new star.   The team event was played in the Rolzaal
at the Binnenhof from 23 vii until 5 viii 1928.} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 d5
