Botvinnik in the hands of Dückstein. It made little difference for the Soviet
Union in group 1. The Netherlands did not qualify in the same group, despite
the great scores by Euwe and Donner. The bronze medalists of Hungary lost to
Columbia in group three and did not make it to final A.   Argentina was among
the twelve countries in final A. Only participants of the Argentinian
