leads to the game.}) 8... dxc3 9. Qxg7 Rg8 10. Qxh7 Nbc6 11. Nf3 Qc7 12. Bb5 $5
(12. Bf4 $1 Bd7 13. Be2 {was played in Unzicker - Dückstein, Zürich 1959.})
12... Bd7 13. O-O $5 ({An alternative is} 13. Bf4 O-O-O 14. O-O {
